long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Bring Luffy’s graffiti art to life with this 4K live wallpaper, featuring a clock and Google search bar on your new tab.

Celebrate the vibrant spirit of Monkey D. Luffy with the Luffy Graffiti 4K live wallpaper. This extension brings a unique and artistic twist to your Chrome new tab, featuring graffiti-style artwork of Luffy in stunning detail. The dynamic background highlights the energy and creativity of the One Piece universe, making it perfect for fans who appreciate both street art and adventure. The minimalist design includes a sleek clock and Google search bar, blending functionality with bold, expressive visuals. Add some pirate flair to your screen with this lively and creative live wallpaper.
